06-02T13:42:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名<br />\n<br />\n內亂到咁 真係第一次見<br />\n由上到下 都公開屌來屌去<br />\n<br />\n仲好像搵球迷打球員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f8d5b3003b0ba39d7a35cfca4fe24c37bddb25a3","tid":687422,"uid":111425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T13:42:25.000Z","msg":"有冇新聞睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a2b1bbd8dd422a24b6e4bc5bee8ff63a3f84ca2","tid":687422,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T13:48:55.000Z","msg":"個主席癲左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7138954f609f604c0979bdc7b7b86cef73c510e","tid":687422,"uid":92603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T13:58:52.000Z","msg":"有冇source?"},{"pid":"393d03df2f56d4e5c931b595cf7fe0c17522ded4","tid":687422,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T14:02:20.000Z","msg":"之前話要雪晒成隊正選"},{"pid":"019f364b930e52b9d791977a768c0c6ab1e50d9c","tid":687422,"uid":13879,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T14:04:18.000Z","msg":"之前歐霸對馬體會主席屌球員唔盡力"},{"pid":"b2c258dd0400b3b37302dc849d1ac65d0f963a6f","tid":687422,"uid":10338,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T14:21:38.000Z","msg":"一群士砵亭球迷周二闖入球隊訓練場，干擾球隊操練並襲擊球員和職員，導致包括荷蘭前鋒巴斯杜斯等部份職球員受傷，士砵亭其後發表聲明作出譴責。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，周二約有50名持有棍棒或腰帶等武器的蒙面球迷闖入士砵亭的訓練中心，襲擊球員和職員，甚至大肆破壞更衣室。除了巴斯杜斯頭部受傷，據悉教練捷西斯、葡萄牙國腳魯爾柏迪斯奧、威廉卡維奴，阿根廷的馬高斯阿古拿、洛迪高巴達利亞等都受到襲擊。警方其後拘留了21名嫌犯。<br />\n<br />\n士砵亭正備戰下周日對艾維斯的葡盃決賽。該隊周日在葡超煞科戰以1:2不敵馬里迪莫，只能獲聯賽第三名，或因失落聯賽次名及下季歐聯資格而令球迷不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180516/large/1526432176_d5c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180516%2Flarge%2F1526432176_d5c8.jpg&h=21e001ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180516/small/1526432175_40cc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180516%2Fsmall%2F1526432175_40cc.jpg&h=a90029cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cefa4543d9facc9261dab8466d1f40a08ba82d43","tid":687422,"uid":10338,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T14:22:40.000Z","msg":"一班士砵亭激進球迷喺上個禮拜二闖入球隊訓練場，襲擊同埋騷擾職球員，前鋒巴斯杜斯頭部仲搞到受傷淌血。葡萄牙傳媒報道，士砵亭主帥佐治捷西斯已掌握證據，證明主席般奴卡華奴係事件幕後黑手。報道指，上月六日士砵亭喺歐霸對陣馬德里體育會之後，般奴卡華奴就同邀進球迷組織Juve Leo嘅負責人會面。不過般奴卡華奴曾發出聲明，否認同Juve Leo有接觸。佐治捷西斯就話，佢已掌握卡華奴策劃事件嘅證據，並計劃採取法律行動。據此前報道，般奴卡華奴早前曾同麾下球員爆發罵戰，又將合共19名球員停賽。近日事件又再升級，般奴卡華奴上個禮拜一仲將佐治捷西斯同埋佢嘅教練團隊處以停賽，雙方關係進一步決裂"},{"pid":"e9c51d54f431bec89029b682a63d00750ef8e1d9","tid":687422,"uid":119135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T14:24:25.000Z","msg":"少林足球咁"},{"pid":"ac3d37a3817183656d5c90eef3641197056e5292","tid":687422,"uid":55,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T14:44:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d66a616a0b46b9f669285c8a4240a2cee459f3e","tid":687422,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T14:47:25.000Z","msg":"抵打啦 馬里迪莫都贏唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53431fed4e8cdafb1d7e336c41a67b9fcd6cd90c","tid":687422,"uid":24423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac3d37a3817183656d5c90eef3641197056e5292","tid":687422,"uid":55,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T14:44:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T14:48:19.000Z","msg":"打會員就okay"},{"pid":"c1942d357af1eaff1ab0872594b9dd849bcab9a7","tid":687422,"uid":92278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:03:17.000Z","msg":"打假波抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e422a278706538ad17be47da519a566003763f8","tid":687422,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:23:08.000